STANCE

STANCE will change your current fighting stance. Different stances
provide different benefits or penalties, these have been left up
to you to experiment with and find what works best for you.

The available stances, and their level requirements, are listed
below.

NAME               CLASS/LEVEL
---------------------------------------------------------
Adventurer         None
Mage               Mag > 50 [or ] Psi > 60 [or ] Cle > 70
Ninja              Ass > 30
Shadows            Ass > 30 [or ] Mon > 65
Essence            Mon > 20 [or ] Kni > 45
Beast              Mon > 10 [or ] Kni > 35
Flame              Mon > 45
Spirit             Mon > 60
Void               Mon > 70
Dragon             Mon > 79 [and] Kni > 79
Snake              Mon > 70 [and] Kni > 70
Wizard             Sor > 20 [or ] Nec > 40 [or ] Mon > 60
Magi               Adept > 10
